					<div class="counter-section">
						<h5 class="section-title">Overview</h5>

						<p>
							As part of any process for filling the form service is available
							in the AYUSH Education Portal. Some process needs to <b>Sign
								In</b> from the protal.
						</p>

						<h5 class="section-title">Step-by-Step Guide</h5>
						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 1: </span>Access the portal
							<a href="https://ayushedu.bisag-n.gov.in/AYUSH_EDU"
								class="custom-link" target="_blank">https://ayushedu.bisag-n.gov.in/AYUSH_EDU</a>
							and click on <b>Sign In</b> button.
						</p>

						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="admin/assets/img/module_guide_img/main_portal/signin_process/ncism-admission-1.png"
								alt="signin-common-1" title="signin-common-1" class="img-fluid">
						</div>

						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 2: </span>We taking an
							example as a Sign In process with Faculty category. Faculty will
							receive an email from Ayush Education Portal. Please mention that
							you need to choose particular category for Sign In. Now, Select
							Category – Faculty and further steps of Aadhaar verify is
							following below.
						</p>
						<p>Carefully reviewing the steps and instructions given on the
							sign-in screen you may proceed further by clicking the “Aadhaar
							Verify” button as per the prescribed process.</p>

						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="admin/assets/img/module_guide_img/main_portal/signin_process/nch-faculty-1.gif"
								alt="signin-aadhaarverify-2" title="signin-aadhaarverify-2"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>
						<h5>Steps Instruction after clicking on Aadhaar Verify:</h5>
						<ul>
							<li>Please click on the Aadhaar Verify button below.</li>
							<li>You will be redirected to the Sign In to your account
								via DigiLocker form on Meri Pehchaan Portal.</li>
							<li>Fill in your details using appropriate credentials and
								sign in.</li>
							<li>If you are a new user, you need to sign up for Meri
								Pehchaan.</li>
							<li>DigiLocker will send an OTP to your registered mobile
								number(XXXXXX1234) and Email(dummy**@gmail.com).</li>
							<li>Click on Allow to access the DigiLocker document with
								the Single Window System.</li>
							<li>Finally, You will be signed in according to your user's
								category.</li>
							<li>Finally, You will be signed in according to your user's
								category.</li>
							<li>Upon completion of the final step, you will be
								automatically redirected to the dashboard screen.</li>
						</ul>

