							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 3: </span>Sign In Cases
						</p>

						<p class="custom-case">
							<span class="custom-case-title">Case 1: </span>Faculty is Sign In
							for the first time in the portal, Faculty has to change the
							password will be mandatory so Faculty will be redirected to
							Change Password Screen.
						</p>


						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="admin/assets/img/module_guide_img/main_portal/signin_process/nch-faculty-2.png"
